import React from 'react'
import {Box, AppBar, Container, Typography, Button, Toolbar} from "@mui/material"
import {Link, useNavigate} from 'react-router-dom'

export default function Navbar() {
  
    const navigate=useNavigate();

    return (
    <Box sx={{flexGrow: 1}}>
        <AppBar position='static' color='transparent' >
            <Container>
                <Toolbar>
                    <Typography sx={{flexGrow: 1}}>
                        <Link to="/">Notas Alecs</Link>
                    </Typography>
                    <Button variant="contained" color='primary' onClick={() => ("/tasks/new")}>
                        Nueva Nota
                    </Button>
                </Toolbar>
            </Container>
        </AppBar>
    </Box>
  )
}
